{"tid":1166714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發現真係好多人唔識分\"係\"同\"喺\"","createTime":"2019-05-22T15:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T04:18:58.000Z","uid":91574,"like":142,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fbeea725c61b7939839fc8659c252b0fdf443bb4","tid":1166714,"uid":91574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"以前都唔會咁樣，反而近呢一年唔知係咪因為肥絲成日捉人左左右右，搞到啲人以為口語就=將啲字加個口字邊，將&quot;係&quot;寫做&quot;喺&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都明個&quot;喺&quot;字難打，所以將'喺'打做&quot;係&quot;，其實就冇乜所謂，但我fb ig都好多人將&quot;係&quot;打做&quot;喺&quot;，每次見到都想&quot;喺佢老母&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7TVVmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7TVVmc.jpg&h=4da2bc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjHfVmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjHfVmd.jpg&h=31158602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1ynAme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1ynAme.jpg&h=7eceee87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(sor我有follow名校secret<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n其實&quot;喺&quot;係解&quot;在&quot;<br />\n例句：我今日喺沙田食飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRBsMti.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRBsMti.jpg&h=f93fdc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到啲人係喺不分真係好燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畫蛇添足、多此一舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b521020f0568999751608736c2810bd9c0dc123","tid":1166714,"uid":243181,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:24:21.000Z","ms